Lorna Maseko, a celebrity cook, and soccer star Itumeleng Khune are two of South Africa’s most loved media personalities. Maseko’s style is definitive of the modern woman whose look is comfortable and feminine, with hints of glamour. Khune’s day-to-day look can be described as casual and athletic.  However, he sometimes makes an appearance in a classic black suit. If you’re looking to stand out, here are some style tips to incorporate into your own wardrobe this spring and summer season: Lorna Maseko – Minimal beauty Steal her style Wardrobe Inspiration: Itumeleng Khune - Laid back Steal his style Wardrobe Inspiration: Stockists: Charles and Keith, 011 729 5023 Diesel, 011 783 0882 H&M, h&m.com Mat and May, matandmay.co.za mrp, mrp.com Superbalist, superbalist.com Woolworths, woolworths.co.za